Robin Mattson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Robin_Mattson 0 Robin Mattson (born June 1, 1956) is an American actress. She is best known for her roles on the daytime soap operas General Hospital, Santa Barbara, and All My Children. Robin_Mattson ( born June_1_,_1956 ) is an_American_actress .
